phrases: There are all sorts of mysteries in this world,
like snacks and candy and sweets falling from the sky!
Not the school counselor mimicking Naoe-kun's voice?
I do not think we have any teachers with that particular talent.
I think your skirt might be caught on something.
Oh, so it was an anteater.
Now I cannot get a wife!
I do not think you can get one in the first place.
I will try to find a husband, then.
Well, since you are here, do you want a donut?
But I cannot let many people know about it.
Now you are my partner in crime!
You like sweet things, do not you, Kamikita-san?
It is a small thing, but the fact that it makes me happy is amazing.
That is why sweets are amazing!
If you are happy, then I am happy.
When you make someone happy, you make yourself a little happier too.
If you are happy, I am happy.
If I am happy, you are happy.
And that repeats over and over, making a happiness spiral!
I guess if you really believe in a theory like that, you will end up happy.
I am glad you came here, Naoe-kun.
We are in the same class, but we have never talked before.
I came here to recruit you!
We are forming a baseball team.
We do not have enough members yet, so we are looking for some more.
Is the third baseman a dandelion?
I do not think they could.
No, it is not the plants playing baseball.
We are going to play a casual game of baseball under the blue sky.
No matter how you look at it, Kamikita-san and baseball do not go hand-in-hand.
Hey now, I will give you another.
We formed a baseball team, the Little Busters.
The members, not including Kengo, are
I need carbohydrates for my muscles!
Come on, it is for my muscles!
What is with all the hubbub this early in the morning?
Hey, do not call me an idiot!
I got riled up after reading a band comic.
So you do not actually care what we do?
So forming a baseball team was on the spur of the moment too?
We needed five more members, right?
Let us find them and dedicate our youth to baseball!
What I want to do is not some boring sport like baseball,
but a passionate action battle thing!
What was he trying to do?
I bestow upon you the title...
I doubt there is even one person who would consider picking up baseball in their second year of high school.
Hey, have you seen Natsume Rin?
She is on duty today, but she has not erased the board.
She is probably playing with cats again.
That is all she ever does.
She does not care about anything but herself and those cats.
Just because she is popular with the guys...
Be the first in history to walk on two legs!
I figured you would be here, Rin.
You should not be playing when you are on duty.
No one will like you if you do not do your job.
You are not getting along with the girls in class, right?
So are you friends with any of them?
What is so bad about not having friends?
It is not like I am causing any problems for you!
Are you going to die if I do not have any?
I know we grew up together and that we can hang out now,
but once we graduate, you know...
There is a message on here.
There is a secret in this world.
Your first task: Fix the sanitation problem in the boys' dorm storage shack.
It is not from the cat?
We could tail Lennon and find out who wrote it.
But that would not be fair.
Wait, Rin, are you going to do this task?
I just need to clear the task, right?
This is just some childish prank.
It might be someone trying to mess with you.
What they want to tell us.
I could see the excitement in Rin's eyes.
Almost as if she was a cat, chasing after the tuft on a cat wand.
What kind of secret is there in this world?
All there is here is an unchanging everyday life.
If I had to name something that made me uneasy, it would be...
A sleep disorder I have had since I was young.
I do not know when I will suffer an attack and fall asleep.
I am thinking of making you the fourth batter.
Having the weakest-looking player grow into the best clean-up hitter is absolutely necessary in any plot!
We cannot have a fourth batter yet.
Anyway, get a load of these!
We are going to fix the boys' dorm's sanitation problem!
So this is the storage shack?
The last time they cleaned this place was probably before the Meiji Restoration.
You are seriously going to do this, Rin?
Well, it is not like cleaning the place is a bad thing, but...
So why the hell do I have to help clean this place?
You know, I have allergies that make me want to dance and yell,
whenever I try to clean stuff.
Wow, this place is full of treasures!
The entire series is in here!
We are trying to clean up here!
Do not take them out of the box!
I have decided to be recruited!
I would be really happy to help you out, Naoe-kun!
Wait, does that mean you are joining the Little Busters?
Natsume-san, you are a member too?
Let us do our best at this baseball thing!
I am fine, I am fi
Why do you have mittens on?
Do not you need these for baseball?
Sorry, but those are not the kind you use in baseball.
But I want to do something before I become a member.
So what she wanted to do...
It will be good for my muscles.
You are going to finish the task, are not you?
I did not think we would get it this clean...
I sure did a good job!
We finished your task thanks to Kamikita-san.
Now that the baseball team's room is nice and clean, let us play baseball!
This is not the baseball team's room.
So bad that I cannot undo the furrows in my brow.
Well, it looks like she has drive...
All I see is a big liability to the team.
Let us give her a membership test.
If we say she fails, we gracefully turn her down, and that will be the end of it.
Your words were so righteous that they rang deep in my soul.
Are not these kinds of tests usually for physical aptitude?
In that case, let us start with...
Oh man, I cannot bear to watch this.
Now you should not have any problems.
I am pretty sure there is...
So this is a real glove...
Alright, this is the last question.
Kamikita Komari, you have everything it takes to play baseball!
Starting today, you are a member of the Little Busters!
I hope we can be good friends!
Call me Komari-chan if you would like!
I am not used to this!
She is just not used to it.
She does not know how to interact with you.
She is never been called Rin-chan, after all.
Wait, so does that make me Muscle-chan?
I thought it sounded pretty good too.
The same wish crossed my mind again.
If only every day could be like this forever...
Just like always, it came without warning.
I was disconnected from this world.
I was invited to a mysterious tea party!
Who is trying to seduce you, Riki?
hitori ga tsurai kara futatsu no te wo tsunaida
It was too hard for one to do, so two of us held hands
futari ja samishii kara wa ni natte te wo tsunaida
